+# The "Examination of Religions" part 2: "Volodimer's sending envoys to various peoples" – set in the year 6495 (987/8){{sfn|Ostrowski|2006|p=568}}
+# The "Kherson/Korsun Legend" part 1: "the capture of Kherson resulting in negotiations for the hand of the sister of the co-emperors of Byzantium"{{sfn|Ostrowski|2006|p=568}} – set in the year 6496 (988/9){{sfn|Ostrowski|2006|p=569}}
