+The ''[[Primary Chronicle]]''{{'}}s account of Volodimer's conversion{{sfn|Ostrowski|2006|p=567}} is a compilation of four distinct conversion stories loosely tied together:{{sfn|Ostrowski|2006|p=567}}
+# The "Examination of Religions" part 1: "the missionaries coming to Kyiv"{{sfn|Ostrowski|2006|p=568}}
+# The "Examination of Religions" part 2: "Volodimer's sending envoys to various peoples"{{sfn|Ostrowski|2006|p=568}}
